<div class=3D"outline-text-2" id=3D"text-1">
<p>
Archive: <a href=3D"https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/ann-opam-minver-0-2-0-autom=
atically-determine-minimum-dependency-versions/18328/1">https://discuss.oca=
ml.org/t/ann-opam-minver-0-2-0-automatically-determine-minimum-dependency-v=
ersions/18328/1</a>
</p>
