<p>
Other noteworthy fixes include that <code>configure.sh</code> <a href=3D"ht=
tps://github.com/Solo5/solo5/pull/645">now checks for the C compiler versio=
n</a> to be at least GCC in version 9 or clang in version 10. The <code>sol=
o5-hvt-debug</code> crashed since too strict seccomp rules were applied (si=
nce solo5 0.11.0) - thanks to Felix Solcher for opening the <a href=3D"http=
s://github.com/Solo5/solo5/issues/643">issue</a>, and again Romain Calascib=
etta for the <a href=3D"https://github.com/Solo5/solo5/pull/644">fix</a>.
</p>

<p>
Awaiting opam-repository merge at <a href=3D"https://github.com/ocaml/opam-=
repository/pull/30182">https://github.com/ocaml/opam-repository/pull/30182<=
/a>
</p>
